request.description:
**Paste this JSON into the WebSocket message input:**

```json
{
  "type": "user.message",
  "payload": {
    "message": "Can you expand the section about AI pair programming tools?"
  }
}
```

Server responds with streaming `user.chat_response` events.

**Paste this JSON into the WebSocket message input:**

```json
{
  "type": "user.approve",
  "payload": {
    "comment": "Looks good, generate the final report."
  }
}
```

Server responds with `user.approval_accepted`, then streams `workflow.state_changed` events as the report is finalized.

**Paste this JSON into the WebSocket message input:**

```json
{
  "type": "user.request_changes",
  "payload": {
    "changes": {
      "sections_to_expand": ["Methodology"],
      "general_feedback": "Add more quantitative data."
    }
  }
}
```

Server responds with `user.changes_accepted`, then resumes the review cycle.

**Paste this JSON into the WebSocket message input:**

```json
{
  "type": "user.cancel",
  "payload": {}
}
```

Server responds with `user.cancel_accepted`.

